node.title: Three people arrested over 2019 death of man found in Hamilton garden
node.description: Police have arrested three people in relation to the death of Joshua Terrey, who was found dead in a Hamilton garden in 2019.
node.content:
["Police have arrested three people in relation to the death of Joshua Terrey, who was found dead in a Hamilton garden in 2019.", "", "
File image. Photo: RNZ / Richard Tindiller
", "A Hamilton woman, 24, a Hamilton man, 60, and a Waihi woman, 45, have all been charged with kidnapping and injuring with intent.", "They will appear in the Hamilton District Court on 12 April.", ""Police wish to thank the community and the victim's family for their support which has enabled Police to hold these people to account several years on from Josh's death," a statement said.", "Terrey was found deceased in a garden at the Western Community Centre in Nawton, Hamilton on December 1 2019."]
